Package org.anchoranalysis.plugin.mpp.experiment.bean.segment

Class SegmentMarksFromImage

Object
AnchorBean<Task<T,​S>>
Task<MultiInput,​ExperimentState>
SegmentMarksFromImage
public class SegmentMarksFromImage
extends Task<MultiInput,​ExperimentState>
Segments an image into a collection of Marks.

The following outputs are produced:

Output NameDefault?Description
marksyesThe segmented outcome as serialized XML using XStream.
outlineyesA RGB image showing outline-colored segmented marks on a background.
solidnoA RGB image showing solidly-colored segmented marks on a background.
any outputs produced by SegmentIntoMarks in segment.
inherited from Task
Author:
Owen Feehan
